  "description": "Enumeration of log levels for categorizing log entries.\nFollows standard logging severity levels from lowest to highest.",
  "title": "Enum LogLevel",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_LogLevel'>Enum LogLevel    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/LogLevel.cs#L36'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Enumeration of log levels for categorizing log entries.\nFollows standard logging severity levels from lowest to highest.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public enum LogLevel : byte</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>Trace = 0</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Trace level: Most detailed, for diagnostic information.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Debug = 1</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Debug level: Information useful for development and debugging.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Info = 2</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Info level: General informational messages.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Warning = 3</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Warning level: Warning messages for potentially problematic situations.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Error = 4</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Error level: Error messages for serious problems.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Critical = 5</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Critical level: Critical errors requiring immediate attention.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>None = 255</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">None: Special level to disable logging.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
